  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="7692134">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/7692134/" class="title-link">阿伦特和她的“政治的”</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-7692134"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/3475373/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u3475373-15.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/3475373/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">苏横</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar30 main-title-rating" title="还行"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2015-12-15"
      class="main-meta">2015-12-15 18:41:51</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_7692134_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  上次读了菲利普·汉森写的《阿伦特传》，虽然没有全部读完——翻译还是有些问题的，但是对阿伦特和她的政治观念有了点大致的了解，算是小小的心得吧，写下来，希望有心人看了之后，可以有所启发。   汉森曾在书中写到“虚假”的政治是“赋予公共生活以形式而没有给予其实质的内...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_7692134_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_7692134_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





